WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 13=

01:38.660 --> 01:41.780
(Xuanwu Altar, Dungeon)

01:45.740 --> 01:47.980
(Li Sect, Xing)

01:47.980 --> 01:48.820
Hurry.

01:48.840 --> 01:49.740
Come on, open up!

01:50.210 --> 01:51.410
Can't get it open.

01:54.330 --> 01:55.290
What a useless door!

01:55.660 --> 01:56.770
This is driving me crazy.

02:00.290 --> 02:01.410
So filthy in here.

02:04.900 --> 02:05.740
Xing.

02:06.620 --> 02:07.460
Listen!

02:07.470 --> 02:08.570
Using me to threaten You Guanyue

02:08.570 --> 02:09.660
is totally useless.

02:09.750 --> 02:10.690
If he dares back down,

02:10.720 --> 02:11.620
I'll tear him a new one!

02:17.060 --> 02:18.390
Xing, I'm here to rescue you.

02:18.410 --> 02:19.250
Come with me.

02:20.290 --> 02:21.130
Go.

02:24.940 --> 02:26.860
(Master of Xuanwu Altar, Xiong Qianjin)

02:27.220 --> 02:28.100
I'd like to see

02:28.500 --> 02:29.340
who this

02:29.500 --> 02:30.610
spy is.

02:33.960 --> 02:34.900
Find a chance to escape.

03:03.540 --> 03:04.380
Where's Xing?

03:04.450 --> 03:05.290
She ran away.

03:05.290 --> 03:06.170
Where to?

03:06.380 --> 03:07.220
You didn't see her?

03:42.450 --> 03:43.290
Get up!

03:46.260 --> 03:47.100
Go!

03:58.910 --> 04:00.380
Mu Qingyan seized the Qinglong Altar.

04:00.610 --> 04:02.780
Nie Zhe will surely set up
heavy guards all around.

04:03.380 --> 04:05.060
We need a foolproof plan first.

04:06.010 --> 04:07.850
Say our family works at
the Qinglong Altar,

04:08.040 --> 04:09.820
and we're here to
persuade them to surrender.

04:10.950 --> 04:11.940
The demon sect is ruthless.

04:12.780 --> 04:14.100
They won't spare innocents,

04:14.450 --> 04:15.290
let alone relatives.

04:16.340 --> 04:17.460
This plan is too risky.

04:18.900 --> 04:19.900
Stories always say,

04:20.100 --> 04:21.140
victory favors the bold.

04:21.610 --> 04:23.050
Only the brave win head-on fights.

04:24.050 --> 04:25.580
You'll never know unless you try.

04:26.340 --> 04:27.180
Zhao.

04:27.190 --> 04:28.980
You can't survive out there
just by storybooks.

04:30.810 --> 04:32.410
Books pave the way for journeys.

04:32.730 --> 04:33.570
Why wouldn't it work?

04:34.250 --> 04:35.090
Hurry up and go.

04:43.410 --> 04:44.430
- A ghost!
- Don't run!

04:44.460 --> 04:45.300
A ghost!

04:45.660 --> 04:47.060
- Miss!
-Ghost! Ghost!

04:47.100 --> 04:47.940
Miss.

04:48.490 --> 04:49.330
Miss!

04:54.020 --> 04:55.100
(No inner power at all)

04:56.140 --> 04:56.980
Calm down.

04:56.990 --> 04:58.020
What kind of ghost was it?

04:58.610 --> 04:59.450
Take your time.

04:59.900 --> 05:01.250
I saw a bunch of walking ghosts.

05:01.580 --> 05:02.420
Yellow faces.

05:02.730 --> 05:03.570
White eyes.

05:03.810 --> 05:04.700
They walk like this.

05:06.540 --> 05:07.380
It terrified me.

05:08.700 --> 05:09.850
Could it be the corpse slaves?

05:10.070 --> 05:11.700
Could Nie Zhe be up to
his old tricks again,

05:11.930 --> 05:13.220
refining corpse slaves once more?

05:14.250 --> 05:15.090
Who are you?

05:17.660 --> 05:19.220
Why are you wearing my dress?

05:20.920 --> 05:22.050
Village chief gave it to me.

05:22.850 --> 05:23.690
Grandpa?

05:23.780 --> 05:24.620
You're Xing?

05:24.980 --> 05:25.820
Enough.

05:25.820 --> 05:26.850
I need to tell Grandpa quickly.

05:26.850 --> 05:27.810
If Xiong Qianjin comes for me,

05:27.810 --> 05:28.730
everyone will be in trouble.

05:29.810 --> 05:30.650
Xing!

05:32.140 --> 05:33.100
We'll go with you.

05:58.020 --> 05:59.610
Where did you hide Xing?

06:01.170 --> 06:02.010
No idea.

06:02.410 --> 06:03.370
I don't know.

06:03.370 --> 06:04.210
No idea.

06:06.900 --> 06:08.460
Tell me where you hid Xing!

06:12.220 --> 06:13.370
Tell me!

06:16.460 --> 06:17.300
If you do,

06:17.810 --> 06:19.170
then you won't die.

06:19.170 --> 06:20.780
Xiong Qianjin, you scoundrel!

06:21.100 --> 06:21.940
I...

06:25.920 --> 06:26.820
Keep this safe for me.

06:27.540 --> 06:28.540
Zhao, what are you doing?

06:28.810 --> 06:29.650
Don't worry, Yuzhi.

06:29.920 --> 06:30.820
Gotta disguise myself.

06:39.460 --> 06:40.490
Where did you hide Xing?

06:41.050 --> 06:43.100
I don't know. I really don't know.

06:50.780 --> 06:51.900
You all wanna die, huh?

06:53.810 --> 06:54.650
Speak!

07:00.980 --> 07:01.820
Stop!

07:05.810 --> 07:06.650
Xiong Qianjin.

07:06.830 --> 07:07.930
Aren't you here to catch me?

07:11.660 --> 07:12.500
I'll go with you.

07:12.900 --> 07:13.740
Let them go.

07:26.570 --> 07:28.250
Grandpa, don't be scared.

07:28.370 --> 07:29.210
It'll be fine.

07:37.220 --> 07:38.140
Xing.

07:38.340 --> 07:40.220
They killed Wang.

07:40.220 --> 07:41.460
Poor Wang.

07:41.460 --> 07:43.410
He barely lived in his new house.

07:43.410 --> 07:44.250
Shut up!

07:48.250 --> 07:49.090
Big lug.

07:49.120 --> 07:50.250
Aren't you gonna take me away?

07:50.340 --> 07:51.380
What are you stalling for?

07:53.490 --> 07:55.220
I hate being called a big lug.

07:55.900 --> 07:56.900
If you try to run again,

07:57.540 --> 07:58.490
I'll break your legs!

08:00.170 --> 08:01.010
Come on.

08:01.370 --> 08:02.250
Take them all back!

08:02.730 --> 08:04.100
Wait.

08:04.460 --> 08:06.090
Move, hurry!

08:10.140 --> 08:10.980
Hurry up!

08:12.730 --> 08:13.570
Hurry!

08:24.220 --> 08:26.050
Xing.

08:26.050 --> 08:27.370
Grandpa, Grandpa.

08:27.870 --> 08:29.290
Go to Qinglong Altar for reinforcements.

08:29.810 --> 08:30.650
I'll save Zhao.

08:37.770 --> 08:38.610
Go! Hurry!

08:40.340 --> 08:41.300
Keep up, back there!

08:42.130 --> 08:42.970
Hurry!

08:44.420 --> 08:45.260
Hurry up!

08:47.420 --> 08:48.260
Go!

08:55.530 --> 08:56.370
Go!

08:56.580 --> 08:57.420
Keep up!

09:02.980 --> 09:03.820
Hurry!

09:10.300 --> 09:11.140
Hurry!

09:13.340 --> 09:14.180
What are you doing?

09:15.580 --> 09:17.130
You nearly blinded me.

09:17.220 --> 09:18.490
One day, I'll take your eyes out!

09:18.730 --> 09:20.060
Master Xiong.

09:26.650 --> 09:27.490
Lady Sun.

09:28.010 --> 09:28.890
It's so late.

09:29.220 --> 09:31.130
What brings you to such a remote place?

09:32.180 --> 09:33.610
Picking flowers for the Chief.

09:34.850 --> 09:37.100
These flowers need night dew

09:37.650 --> 09:38.850
to have their medicinal effect.

09:39.370 --> 09:40.420
- Move quickly!
- Yes.

09:54.460 --> 09:55.370
Who are you?

09:56.150 --> 09:57.420
I'm a maid of the Qinglong Altar.

09:57.770 --> 09:58.610
Xing.

09:58.610 --> 09:59.730
Your face is covered in dirt,

10:00.180 --> 10:01.700
but your eyes are beautiful.

10:05.980 --> 10:06.940
Master Xiong.

10:07.460 --> 10:09.770
Why not give this girl to me?

10:10.890 --> 10:11.730
This...

10:12.420 --> 10:13.260
Madam.

10:13.420 --> 10:14.770
The strategist asked for this girl.

10:15.180 --> 10:16.940
I'm afraid I can't explain it to him.

10:18.610 --> 10:19.450
Fine then.

10:23.100 --> 10:23.940
Farewell, Madam.

10:25.890 --> 10:27.220
Quit staring! Move!

10:38.820 --> 10:39.660
Mr. Mu.

10:40.720 --> 10:41.980
The village is completely empty.

10:42.250 --> 10:43.420
Xing is nowhere to be found.

10:43.820 --> 10:45.010
Where exactly did Xing go?

11:10.980 --> 11:11.820
Find them.

11:34.460 --> 11:37.460
(Youming Path)

11:41.940 --> 11:42.780
Move!

12:04.460 --> 12:05.300
My leg!

12:07.220 --> 12:08.060
My leg.

12:09.490 --> 12:10.940
I can't go on either.

12:13.580 --> 12:14.420
What are you doing?

12:14.750 --> 12:15.690
Are you trying to die?

12:16.250 --> 12:17.700
My old leg injury is acting up again.

12:17.720 --> 12:18.890
- I can't walk anymore.
- Get up.

12:19.340 --> 12:20.460
My knee's acting up again.

12:20.940 --> 12:21.780
I can't move.

12:22.130 --> 12:22.980
Stand up!

12:22.980 --> 12:24.100
Get up now, hear me?

12:25.700 --> 12:26.540
Dare to run?

12:26.970 --> 12:27.980
- Come back!
- After her!

12:28.100 --> 12:28.940
Catch her!

12:30.340 --> 12:31.180
Stop!

12:31.730 --> 12:32.570
Don't run!

12:40.220 --> 12:41.060
Stop!

12:42.530 --> 12:43.370
Over there!

12:59.700 --> 13:02.180
This is the Poison Swarm Array
aunt encountered back then.

13:05.370 --> 13:06.850
Touch the array's trigger,

13:10.130 --> 13:12.420
and deadly venomous swarm
will swarm you.

13:13.460 --> 13:14.300
Run!

13:14.460 --> 13:15.340
Once they sting you,

13:15.340 --> 13:16.370
(Spring and Blossoms)

13:16.370 --> 13:17.370
you'll die for sure.

13:18.300 --> 13:19.140
(This array)

13:19.650 --> 13:21.610
(is just like the Poison Swarm Array)

13:21.940 --> 13:22.850
(aunt told me about.)

13:29.060 --> 13:30.700
(This must be the trigger spot.)

13:33.460 --> 13:35.490
As long as I apply
the Bee-Repelling Powder,

13:36.060 --> 13:37.700
the venomous bees will stay far away.

13:43.740 --> 13:45.180
There she is! Don't let her get away!

14:12.060 --> 14:12.900
Stay still!

14:36.650 --> 14:37.490
You guys go, now.

14:38.180 --> 14:40.130
But what about Miss Feng?

14:40.390 --> 14:41.330
I'll get you out first.

14:42.150 --> 14:43.490
This is what Miss Feng wanted too.

14:44.580 --> 14:45.890
Alright, let's go.

14:46.010 --> 14:46.940
Go, let's go.

14:47.370 --> 14:48.210
- Go.
- Go!

14:48.610 --> 14:49.490
Hurry, go now!

14:55.730 --> 14:56.570
Who are you?

15:07.940 --> 15:08.780
You're not Xing.

15:22.940 --> 15:23.850
(Oh no.)

15:24.220 --> 15:27.420
(She fed me softening powder.)

15:33.010 --> 15:33.850
Don't try any tricks.

15:34.820 --> 15:35.660
Move!

15:41.820 --> 15:46.220
(Li Sect, EightClaw Prison)

16:13.650 --> 16:14.490
Speak.

16:15.030 --> 16:16.020
Who are your accomplices?

16:16.940 --> 16:18.010
Six Sects of Beichen,

16:18.770 --> 16:19.700
or Mu Qingyan?

16:22.580 --> 16:23.730
I don't know them.

16:24.650 --> 16:26.730
I'm just a junior from the Qingzhu Gang.

16:27.220 --> 16:28.130
I came to the Li Sect

16:28.940 --> 16:30.340
to seek refuge with a relative.

16:31.130 --> 16:32.140
Qingzhu Gang?

16:32.510 --> 16:33.570
Our Qingzhu Gang

16:33.730 --> 16:35.890
is a small sect by the Canglang River.

16:36.580 --> 16:37.530
The leader passed away.

16:38.180 --> 16:39.250
And the sect disbanded.

16:40.730 --> 16:41.730
I had nowhere else to go.

16:42.650 --> 16:44.100
So I came here to find my relative.

16:49.890 --> 16:51.130
Why did you pretend to be Xing?

16:54.490 --> 16:55.820
I got lost in the forest.

16:56.730 --> 16:58.300
The villagers found me

16:58.300 --> 16:59.140
and took me in.

17:00.130 --> 17:01.370
If it weren't for them,

17:02.460 --> 17:03.700
I would've died a long time ago.

17:04.520 --> 17:05.660
My martial arts aren't great,

17:06.530 --> 17:07.420
but I do understand

17:08.520 --> 17:09.460
a small act of kindness

17:09.520 --> 17:11.010
should be repaid with deep gratitude.

17:12.010 --> 17:12.850
Last night,

17:13.420 --> 17:14.730
that so-called Master Xiong

17:15.420 --> 17:16.660
tied up everyone in the village.

17:17.460 --> 17:18.320
He said

17:18.380 --> 17:19.570
if they didn't hand over Xing,

17:19.900 --> 17:21.730
he'd kill every single one of them.

17:24.140 --> 17:26.050
He killed Uncle Wang
right then and there.

17:26.770 --> 17:28.220
It was a horrifying scene.

17:29.330 --> 17:30.940
They saved my life.

17:31.140 --> 17:32.460
How could I stand by and do nothing?

17:34.220 --> 17:35.060
I acted on impulse,

17:36.730 --> 17:37.980
and pretended to be Xing.

17:39.290 --> 17:40.810
Xiong Qianjin.

17:41.570 --> 17:43.730
He used the villagers' lives
to threaten us.

17:45.570 --> 17:46.410
Yeah.

17:47.940 --> 17:49.290
Poor Uncle Wang.

17:49.860 --> 17:51.290
His baby was only three months old.

17:51.810 --> 17:53.940
Aunt Wang cried so hard
she almost fainted.

18:01.940 --> 18:02.780
You're lying.

18:03.420 --> 18:05.460
How could a mere Qingzhu clan disciple

18:05.810 --> 18:07.290
know about the Poison Swarm Array?

18:09.770 --> 18:10.610
Sis.

18:11.940 --> 18:12.980
You don't know.

18:14.250 --> 18:16.050
When our leader was young,

18:16.070 --> 18:17.380
he had an extraordinary experience.

18:18.090 --> 18:19.290
He said he once met a

18:19.290 --> 18:20.860
most amazing female hero.

18:21.860 --> 18:22.810
That heroine

18:23.250 --> 18:24.180
wielded a sword

18:24.620 --> 18:26.010
brighter than the sun.

18:26.460 --> 18:27.300
So mighty.

18:28.220 --> 18:29.330
That array

18:30.010 --> 18:32.180
was taught to our old leader
by the heroine.

18:33.420 --> 18:34.460
Could it be her?

18:35.730 --> 18:37.570
(This person doesn't seem all that bad.)

18:39.090 --> 18:39.930
Sis.

18:40.980 --> 18:41.820
Is this place

18:42.090 --> 18:43.420
where they

18:43.810 --> 18:45.620
turn people into monsters?

18:45.810 --> 18:46.650
What monsters?

18:51.570 --> 18:52.530
The village chief said,

18:53.050 --> 18:54.050
lately in the village,

18:54.380 --> 18:56.660
when the uncles and brothers go hunting,

18:57.230 --> 18:58.900
they keep getting captured
by the Slayer Ghost.

18:59.520 --> 19:01.090
When they come back,
they're turned into

19:01.090 --> 19:02.140
gray-faced, white-eyed monsters.

19:02.860 --> 19:03.940
Slayer Ghost?

19:04.050 --> 19:04.890
Yeah.

19:05.010 --> 19:05.850
It's terrifying.

19:07.140 --> 19:08.700
Neither alive nor dead.

19:09.040 --> 19:10.010
No response when called.

19:10.180 --> 19:11.860
And it suddenly
goes mad and bites people.

19:12.770 --> 19:13.610
Sis.

19:25.420 --> 19:26.730
You're refining a corpse slave.

19:27.980 --> 19:29.330
Back then, Master lost his mind,

19:29.920 --> 19:31.420
and insisted on refining corpse slaves.

19:31.860 --> 19:33.900
Our fellow disciples
either died or scattered.

19:34.050 --> 19:35.140
Have you forgotten all that?

19:36.380 --> 19:38.380
Why are you making these
evil things again?

19:40.460 --> 19:41.300
I haven't forgotten.

19:42.490 --> 19:43.910
But this is the Chief's order.

19:45.430 --> 19:46.620
I have no choice but to obey.

19:47.230 --> 19:48.490
The ambush on the Six Sects earlier

19:48.860 --> 19:50.660
cost the Demonic Camp heavy losses.

19:51.180 --> 19:52.700
Mu Qingyan is advancing fast,

19:53.420 --> 19:55.140
and the sect is severely short-handed.

19:55.380 --> 19:56.900
I had no other option.

19:56.910 --> 19:58.620
But you can't
use innocent villagers' lives.

19:59.520 --> 20:01.700
Their families have supported
the Li Sect for generations.

20:02.330 --> 20:03.730
The Li Sect should protect them,

20:03.940 --> 20:05.490
not refine them into corpses.

20:08.380 --> 20:11.330
That village has secretly
sided with the Six Sects,

20:11.380 --> 20:12.860
passing them information.

20:12.860 --> 20:13.700
They must be dealt with.

20:18.010 --> 20:18.940
Fengge.

20:19.140 --> 20:19.980
Don't worry.

20:21.090 --> 20:22.490
For those loyal to the Li Sect,

20:22.940 --> 20:24.810
we will protect them well.

20:35.660 --> 20:36.500
Fengge.

20:38.660 --> 20:40.180
I will investigate myself

20:41.250 --> 20:42.570
whether they betrayed the Li Sect.

20:57.220 --> 20:58.060
Find the one

20:58.530 --> 21:00.180
who leaked the news to Elder Hu.

21:01.940 --> 21:02.780
Kill them.

21:03.530 --> 21:04.370
Understood.

21:23.250 --> 21:24.090
Peng bird.

21:57.770 --> 21:59.730
(Youming Path)

22:00.380 --> 22:02.050
(EightClaw Prison)

22:19.500 --> 22:25.580
(Guo Zigui)

22:28.730 --> 22:30.090
Guo Zigui.

22:30.700 --> 22:32.050
Uncle Guo.

22:40.420 --> 22:41.660
Mom's the best!

22:41.810 --> 22:43.090
Mom's the best!

22:43.090 --> 22:44.660
Your Uncle Guo might be a bit better.

22:44.660 --> 22:45.940
Mom's never beaten him.

22:46.140 --> 22:47.490
Who's Uncle Guo?

22:48.220 --> 22:50.700
He's the uncle
who grew up with your mom.

22:50.700 --> 22:52.770
And also the junior brother
of mine and your Uncle Qi.

22:52.940 --> 22:54.530
Uncle Qi's junior brother?

22:54.660 --> 22:56.090
Is he also at the Qingque Sect?

23:08.140 --> 23:09.810
We haven't heard from him in years.

23:10.330 --> 23:12.010
Is he dead or alive?

23:12.290 --> 23:13.220
Just tell us already.

23:13.770 --> 23:15.620
Doesn't he know
how much we worry about him?

23:15.980 --> 23:17.770
No news isn't always a bad thing.

23:18.320 --> 23:19.460
Just imagine he's still alive.

23:25.660 --> 23:26.940
Could Uncle Guo

23:27.490 --> 23:28.940
have died here?

23:44.140 --> 23:44.990
Mom,

23:45.130 --> 23:46.860
do you know
why Dad went down the mountain?

23:47.420 --> 23:49.090
He has his reasons for going.

23:49.860 --> 23:51.420
Just focus on your cultivation.

23:51.700 --> 23:52.540
Don't worry about it.

23:53.010 --> 23:54.290
But Fengchi said

23:54.340 --> 23:56.700
Dad suddenly left the mountain
after going to Chunling Cottage

23:56.720 --> 23:57.730
the day before yesterday.

23:58.030 --> 23:59.140
Don't you think that's strange?

23:59.730 --> 24:00.770
And Yuzhi.

24:01.120 --> 24:02.460
I haven't seen him in days either.

24:02.660 --> 24:04.620
I thought he was
still recovering in seclusion.

24:04.980 --> 24:06.490
But when I went to Chuitian Dock today,

24:06.730 --> 24:08.620
there were only
two Guangtian Sect guards left.

24:09.250 --> 24:10.090
They said

24:10.710 --> 24:12.090
he went down to clear his head.

24:12.770 --> 24:13.610
Speaking of which,

24:13.820 --> 24:15.330
I haven't seen Cai Zhao in days either.

24:15.630 --> 24:17.380
Could she have gone down
the mountain too?

24:18.860 --> 24:19.700
No.

24:20.660 --> 24:22.420
Did she actually leave with Yuzhi?

24:22.530 --> 24:23.370
Nonsense.

24:31.860 --> 24:34.290
Yuzhi would never act
so recklessly and disrespectfully

24:34.810 --> 24:35.770
Yuzhi always acts

24:36.140 --> 24:37.530
with caution and propriety,

24:37.700 --> 24:38.660
honorable and upright.

24:39.040 --> 24:40.460
If you still have feelings for him,

24:40.940 --> 24:42.490
don't make wild guesses about him.

24:42.530 --> 24:43.570
It'll only upset him.

24:45.280 --> 24:47.010
I care about his injuries
every single day.

24:47.220 --> 24:48.180
But he

24:49.190 --> 24:50.860
snuck down the mountain
without a word.

24:51.380 --> 24:52.490
Without even telling me.

24:54.330 --> 24:55.170
Lingbo,

24:55.810 --> 24:56.650
I already told you,

24:57.220 --> 24:58.620
he doesn't have feelings for you.

24:59.290 --> 25:00.290
Stop forcing it.

25:03.900 --> 25:04.740
Mom.

25:07.090 --> 25:08.420
We got engaged when I was nine.

25:08.730 --> 25:10.010
It's been ten years.

25:10.220 --> 25:11.620
I've trained hard every single day.

25:11.860 --> 25:13.940
Lived in the Disciples' Dorm
like everyone else.

25:14.140 --> 25:15.530
Just so I could be closer to him.

25:15.810 --> 25:16.730
Hoping that one day,

25:16.920 --> 25:18.490
I'd be worthy of him.
Someone so talented

25:18.660 --> 25:19.940
and extraordinary.

25:21.040 --> 25:22.770
I don't care about
being the Lady of Sect.

25:23.090 --> 25:24.330
I just like him.

25:24.380 --> 25:25.490
I like him so much.

25:25.900 --> 25:26.860
So I keep forcing it!

25:39.980 --> 25:40.820
Cai Zhao!

25:42.250 --> 25:43.090
Not here.

25:44.530 --> 25:45.370
Over there.

25:49.900 --> 25:51.300
- Feicui.
- Feicui!

26:02.460 --> 26:03.300
Where's Cai Zhao?

26:04.010 --> 26:05.810
After that Body Shift incident,

26:05.900 --> 26:08.140
milady's been holding in her anger.

26:08.320 --> 26:09.730
It turns out more than ten years ago,

26:09.730 --> 26:11.460
our Luoying Valley was besieged
by the demon sect,

26:11.460 --> 26:12.770
and we almost all died.

26:13.020 --> 26:15.050
It was all the doing of
the previous Lord of Qingque Sect

26:15.250 --> 26:16.700
and his daughter.

26:17.520 --> 26:18.910
Just thinking about it makes me angry.

26:19.250 --> 26:20.690
This Qingque Sect,

26:20.860 --> 26:22.180
is really not a place to stay.

26:22.570 --> 26:23.610
- You...
- Shut up!

26:23.730 --> 26:24.980
How dare a lowly maid

26:24.980 --> 26:26.250
talk nonsense here?

26:26.810 --> 26:27.650
Just tell me.

26:28.220 --> 26:29.330
Where did Cai Zhao go?

26:31.330 --> 26:32.730
For a disciple of Qingque Sect

26:33.150 --> 26:35.180
to skip class and
sneak down the mountain for no reason

26:35.420 --> 26:37.010
is to show open contempt for the sect

26:37.140 --> 26:38.130
and defiance of the Master.

26:38.420 --> 26:40.380
She deserves severe punishment,
expulsion from the sect!

26:42.490 --> 26:43.330
Speak.

26:43.420 --> 26:44.730
Where exactly has Cai Zhao gone?

26:46.380 --> 26:47.220
Will you talk or not?

26:53.330 --> 26:54.170
Xingjia, Lingbo.

26:54.900 --> 26:55.940
Let's talk this out calmly.

26:56.980 --> 26:57.900
Don't scare Feicui.

26:58.570 --> 26:59.420
Zhuo.

26:59.490 --> 27:00.810
She's just a maid.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.420
A maid is still
a disciple of Luoying Valley.

27:02.920 --> 27:03.930
We're all part of the Jianghu.

27:04.320 --> 27:05.530
We don't judge people by their birth.

27:08.900 --> 27:09.740
Let's go.

27:22.460 --> 27:23.300
Feicui.

27:24.530 --> 27:25.380
Zhuo.

27:26.050 --> 27:26.890
Zhao.

27:27.620 --> 27:28.460
Where exactly is she?

27:29.180 --> 27:30.490
She isn't on the mountain.

27:30.620 --> 27:32.090
But don't worry, Zhuo.

27:32.420 --> 27:33.620
She's with Yuzhi.

27:33.700 --> 27:34.770
She'll be fine.

27:37.380 --> 27:38.330
Zhuo.

27:41.700 --> 27:42.540
Then I'll be off.

28:02.890 --> 28:04.140
I've been waiting for you, Lord.

28:09.420 --> 28:10.270
Yunke.

28:10.330 --> 28:11.250
Come, have some tea.

28:11.530 --> 28:12.370
Shijun.

28:12.470 --> 28:13.620
You left days earlier than me,

28:13.770 --> 28:14.610
so why haven't you

28:14.940 --> 28:16.140
entered the Hanhai Mountains yet?

28:17.460 --> 28:18.530
The entrance is sealed.

28:18.620 --> 28:19.460
Can't get in.

28:20.010 --> 28:20.980
I'm guessing

28:21.090 --> 28:23.700
Mr. Mu and Nie Zhe got into a fight.

28:23.700 --> 28:25.290
Then how do you still
have time to sip tea here?

28:26.810 --> 28:27.770
What's the rush?

28:29.700 --> 28:32.380
When Pingshu was Zhao's age,

28:32.530 --> 28:33.860
she could fight her way in and out

28:33.860 --> 28:35.330
of the Youming Path
multiple times.

28:35.380 --> 28:36.220
Besides,

28:36.290 --> 28:37.660
as long as we lay low,

28:37.700 --> 28:39.050
no one will know their identities.

28:39.230 --> 28:40.170
That just makes it safer.

28:40.800 --> 28:42.260
Come on, come down and have some tea.

28:42.380 --> 28:43.220
Let me tell you,

28:43.380 --> 28:44.900
I spent quite a bit on this tea.

28:45.290 --> 28:46.530
The Spring Equinox Maojian Tea.

28:46.620 --> 28:48.250
One sip is worth ten taels of silver.

28:52.620 --> 28:53.460
Give it a try.

28:58.570 --> 28:59.470
Yunke,

28:59.490 --> 29:00.330
please.

29:05.420 --> 29:06.900
Pingshu wrote earlier that

29:07.460 --> 29:08.770
Zhao kept asking him about

29:09.230 --> 29:10.660
the whereabouts of the Jade Sunflower.

29:11.250 --> 29:12.090
This time,

29:12.150 --> 29:13.570
she went down the mountain with Yuzhi.

29:13.860 --> 29:15.380
Straight for the Hanhai Mountains.

29:16.010 --> 29:17.220
Could the Jade Sunflower

29:17.620 --> 29:18.730
really be in the demon sect?

29:18.980 --> 29:20.290
Knowing Pingshu's personality,

29:20.460 --> 29:22.290
she might have really returned it.

29:26.770 --> 29:29.090
No one knows the two kids
went down the mountain together,

29:29.380 --> 29:30.220
right?

29:30.980 --> 29:32.980
After all, they're both unmarried.

29:32.980 --> 29:33.820
What if...

29:33.820 --> 29:34.770
I came alone this time,

29:34.940 --> 29:36.460
just to keep things quiet.

29:45.290 --> 29:46.140
I only hope

29:46.620 --> 29:48.140
they all stay safe.

29:55.770 --> 29:59.490
(My parents are still alive,
when can I go home?)

30:02.330 --> 30:03.700
(The softening powder)

30:04.460 --> 30:06.090
(is getting stronger.)

30:07.050 --> 30:08.810
(Am I going to die here too?)

30:21.470 --> 30:22.810
You overexerted your mind and spirit

30:23.050 --> 30:24.140
fighting Duan Jiuxiu.

30:24.220 --> 30:25.460
You have stagnant energy in your body.

30:25.730 --> 30:26.980
It needs to be released soon.

30:27.420 --> 30:28.700
There are no medicinal herbs here.

30:29.220 --> 30:30.290
Back at the sect. I'll handle it.

30:30.520 --> 30:32.050
I'll teach you
an internal mindful way.

30:32.090 --> 30:32.950
Try using your energy.

30:33.010 --> 30:35.140
Is this the Mu clan's
secret internal mindful way?

30:35.290 --> 30:36.130
You could say that.

30:36.570 --> 30:38.220
This mindful way
was created by my father.

30:38.420 --> 30:39.980
It's called the Innate Circulation.

30:40.020 --> 30:41.570
It works wonders for
injuries and poison.

30:42.420 --> 30:43.570
If not for this mindful way,

30:43.940 --> 30:44.780
over a year ago,

30:44.880 --> 30:46.250
I would've died in the Hanhai Mountains.

30:50.950 --> 30:52.490
New moon on the third, it gleams bright.

30:54.520 --> 30:55.980
Zhen aligns with Geng, toward the West.

31:00.120 --> 31:01.490
On the eighth day,
Dui with Ding.

31:02.380 --> 31:04.730
The crescent, taut as a silken cord.

31:06.420 --> 31:08.090
On the fifteenth day,
Qian forms complete.

31:09.900 --> 31:12.140
Full and bright,
align with Jia, toward the East.

31:17.180 --> 31:18.460
(It actually seems to work.)

31:20.010 --> 31:21.420
(Finally, there's a way out.)

31:33.700 --> 31:34.540
Who are you?

31:34.700 --> 31:35.940
Have you seen the corpse slaves?

31:36.570 --> 31:37.410
A ghost.

31:38.040 --> 31:39.010
I've never seen a ghost.

31:45.490 --> 31:46.900
We'll see where you can run when you

31:46.900 --> 31:47.740
get to the Underworld.

31:48.420 --> 31:49.490
Kill me.

31:50.220 --> 31:51.770
Then your Chief will never get

31:51.770 --> 31:53.420
the treasure for
his divine skill cultivation.

31:54.010 --> 31:55.050
What treasure?

32:01.660 --> 32:02.500
A month ago,

32:03.180 --> 32:04.020
I…

32:04.180 --> 32:05.420
I ran into three people.

32:05.700 --> 32:06.810
One of them said

32:07.180 --> 32:08.420
he was…

32:09.420 --> 32:10.620
Elder from the Li Sect.

32:11.490 --> 32:13.290
Elder Tianji, Duan Jiuxiu.

32:14.180 --> 32:15.460
Where are they now?

32:15.980 --> 32:18.090
They were killed by people
from the Six Sects of Beichen.

32:18.900 --> 32:19.770
Before they died,

32:20.250 --> 32:21.700
they gave me a bottle of something.

32:21.910 --> 32:23.050
Said it was for cultivating...

32:23.060 --> 32:24.170
It called...

32:25.140 --> 32:26.140
Ziwei Method.

32:26.900 --> 32:27.740
They also said

32:27.860 --> 32:29.900
if I offered this treasure
to the Chief of Li Sect,

32:30.040 --> 32:30.900
I'd get a huge reward.

32:30.980 --> 32:32.660
I'm willing to
hand over that treasure now.

32:33.660 --> 32:34.860
All I ask is that you spare me.

32:35.090 --> 32:35.930
Let me live.

32:37.090 --> 32:38.530
Where is the treasure now?

32:38.770 --> 32:40.660
I hid it in the woods of
the Hanhai Mountains.

32:41.290 --> 32:42.730
I can take you there right now.

32:44.020 --> 32:45.220
Trying to trick me?

32:45.700 --> 32:47.020
Elder Tianji,

32:47.570 --> 32:48.860
such a suspicious person,

32:49.810 --> 32:51.530
would never hand a treasure to

32:51.900 --> 32:53.620
a girl he doesn't even know.

32:53.810 --> 32:55.490
It wasn't Elder Tianji
who gave it to me.

32:56.290 --> 32:57.810
It was someone called

32:58.940 --> 33:00.460
Qinong, a beautiful lady.

33:00.880 --> 33:01.940
She secretly hid it for me.

33:02.220 --> 33:04.490
She said Elder Tianji
had turned against her,

33:05.490 --> 33:07.140
and she couldn't survive anymore.

33:07.530 --> 33:09.940
So she asked me to
pass a message to the Chief.

33:29.420 --> 33:30.460
Bring him up here!

33:32.330 --> 33:33.170
Help me!

33:36.530 --> 33:37.700
Where's the treasure?

33:38.290 --> 33:39.180
If you don't talk,

33:39.460 --> 33:40.620
then I'll throw you in.

33:41.090 --> 33:42.700
So this is how you refine corpse slaves.

33:43.530 --> 33:45.010
You've really lost all humanity!

33:46.050 --> 33:46.890
One.

33:47.090 --> 33:47.930
Two.

34:03.180 --> 34:04.490
If I die, we die together!

34:08.690 --> 34:09.530
Zhao.

34:09.650 --> 34:10.490
Yuzhi.

34:15.860 --> 34:17.460
Zhao, are you hurt?

34:17.650 --> 34:18.490
I'm fine.

34:18.850 --> 34:19.980
Outside attack.

34:20.170 --> 34:21.010
We need to go now.

34:26.260 --> 34:27.100
- Get up.
- Get up.

34:27.530 --> 34:28.570
- Get up.
- Thanks, Miss Feng.

34:28.570 --> 34:29.430
Please, get up.

34:29.490 --> 34:30.610
- Get up.
- Upholding justice

34:30.610 --> 34:32.420
is what we in the Jianghu should do.

34:32.650 --> 34:33.820
No need to stand on ceremony.

34:56.920 --> 34:58.740
Mr. Mu, the forced attack
triggered the mechanism.

34:58.740 --> 34:59.690
This place is collapsing!

35:09.780 --> 35:10.620
Li Yi.

35:11.530 --> 35:12.530
Wasn't he stationed at

35:12.530 --> 35:13.780
the Xuanwu Altar with Yu Huiyin?

35:15.050 --> 35:17.210
So this is
where they make corpse slaves.

35:17.380 --> 35:18.650
Monstrous curs.

35:18.680 --> 35:20.340
How many innocent believers
did they seize?

35:20.420 --> 35:21.820
How many corpse slaves have they made?

35:30.170 --> 35:31.010
Sunshine Blade.

35:33.610 --> 35:34.450
Zhao.

35:35.321 --> 35:45.981
=Generation to Generation=

36:04.741 --> 36:09.151
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

36:09.716 --> 36:14.331
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

36:14.671 --> 36:19.236
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

36:19.761 --> 36:24.061
♪Free to wander in the world♪

36:27.006 --> 36:31.706
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:32.231 --> 36:36.521
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:37.181 --> 36:41.211
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:41.526 --> 36:46.651
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:47.226 --> 36:52.036
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:52.251 --> 36:56.421
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:57.146 --> 37:01.081
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:01.581 --> 37:06.856
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

37:29.586 --> 37:34.716
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:35.081 --> 37:39.451
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:39.716 --> 37:43.846
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:44.031 --> 37:49.606
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
